  "common": {
    "name": {
      "zh": "AS“巨浪”MOD.4 9x39 特种突击步枪",
      "en": "AS VAL MOD.4 9x39 special assault rifle"
    },
    "shortName": {
      "zh": "AS VAL MOD.4",
      "en": "AS VAL MOD.4"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "AS VAL (巨浪) 是中央精密机械工程研究院 (TSNIITochMash) 在上世纪面向俄罗斯军警特别行动单位与侦察小组的需求而开发的一款特种突击步枪，采用一体式消音器设计。MOD.4 为第四代特殊改装版本，拥有以下升级特性：弹匣释放钮经过加大，设置有额外的保险操作杆，还换装了新款定制式拉机柄，方便射手进行操作。由战斗遭遇突击团 (BEAR) 诺文斯克分队成员自行研制。",
      "en": "AS VAL MOD.4 is the fourth special modification of the integrally suppressed assault rifle, intended for Russian special operations units and task groups. The MOD.4 features improved controls: an enlarged magazine release button, additional safety selector lever, and an integrated custom charging handle. Developed by members of the BEAR Norvinsk brigade."
    },
